snippet.authorDisplayName: F A I S A L
snippet.textDisplay:
Dear PCB,

You seriously need to make things better before the fans
start doing the peak bashing, I mean, you call it editing? Come on yar, it’s a
professional league, just look at the editing standards. First of all, you need
to watch the highlights of previous year, they were a hell better than these. Then,
hire a professional editor who knows the basics, cricingif waly iss sy behtr krlety
hain, or atleast hire the previous one. There is a lack of transition, no
smooth commentary, boundaries replays are negligible, some wickets get missed,
no intro like the previous year, no slide of target and toss. And it seems like
a bumpy roller coaster. Abhi bhi time hai please behtar krlein. We want it
number 1!
